   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Rapid Disaster Relief</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Since 2015 Filters for Families has engaged in relief projects in Nepal, Puerto Rico, Peru, and Malawi. As disasters increase in our Project areas there is a need for rapid deployment of urgent items. We need to stock filter units, washable sanitation pads and baby diapers, formula, whistles, solar lights, hygiene &amp; first aid items, and other materials.  The two week window following a disaster is critical, especially for vulnerable populations without reserves.</narrative>
  </description>
